1. Why Mathematics is Important in ML
Mathematics gives precision.
Human language is ambiguous, but mathematics is exact.
Machine learning algorithms require precise definitions and calculations.
Topics like probability, statistics, and linear algebra are essential for AI systems such as GPT and Gemini.
